    <description>
        <p>
            PrusaSlicer is a powerful, lightweight slicing software designed for precision and flexibility in 3D printing.
            Compatible with a wide range of printers and materials, it combines advanced customization options with an efficient,
            streamlined workflow, delivering high-quality results on Linux, macOS, and Windows.
            Developed by Prusa Research, PrusaSlicer is fully open-source, supported by a vibrant community,
            and built on the solid foundation of the Slic3r project, originally created by Alessandro Ranellucci.
        </p>
    </description>
